                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-837" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BETTERIDGE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 152.) I was on duty, and a female told me there had been two females taken for stealing a purse. I found this other purse on the floor, near the window.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
