                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 183.) The prisoner and another were given to me—the prisoner produced this purse from her bosom; and while we were entering the charge, the other officer brought in this other purse.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that her companion had found the purse in the street, and given it to her—she received a good character.)</p>
